<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 01:15:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币交易所 KuCoin 向 CFTC 支付 50 万美元以结束民事案件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/crypto-exchange-kucoin-pays-cftc-500-000-to-end-civil-case</link><description>加密货币交易所 KuCoin 的运营商将支付 50 万美元，以和解美国衍生品监管机构对其运营未注册离岸平台、非法让美国居民进行交易的指控。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5.khmz.KgEo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/crypto-exchange-kucoin-pays-cftc-500-000-to-end-civil-case</guid></item><item><title>拟议的共和党法案针对外国加密货币挖矿硬件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/proposed-gop-bill-targets-foreign-crypto-mining-hardware</link><description>共和党参议员周一公布了一项法案，旨在阻止美国加密货币挖矿公司使用与中国和其他外国对手相关的设备。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijjebIvf72ZE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 22:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/proposed-gop-bill-targets-foreign-crypto-mining-hardware</guid></item><item><title>执法负责人辞职后参议员就加密货币问题向 SEC 提出质询</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/senator-queries-sec-on-crypto-cases-after-enforcement-head-quits</link><description>两名美国参议员希望证券交易委员会主席保罗·阿特金斯解释其执行主任的突然辞职，以及她的离职是否与加密货币案件有关，其中包括涉及特朗普家族企业的案件。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihCjjTkzOkw4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 18:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/senator-queries-sec-on-crypto-cases-after-enforcement-head-quits</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略在连续 13 周购买比特币后被打破</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/saylor-s-strategy-takes-break-after-13-weeks-of-bitcoin-buying</link><description>就在公布筹集 420 亿美元以支持其购买比特币的计划几天后，Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 在连续 13 次每周宣布购买加密货币后暂停了交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSxa0aAGSFxw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 13:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/saylor-s-strategy-takes-break-after-13-weeks-of-bitcoin-buying</guid></item></channel></rss>